title: Mint 10000 $LEX to LexDAO Coop.? 💸
body:
LexDAO Coop. has deployed a Gnosis Safe multi-sig. (3/5) , viewable: https://gnosis-safe.io/app/#/safes/0xEA693e18154C98cd9E3014C6Ba1e89956a929F4A/balances 🔒

LexDAO Collective, represented by $LEX and stakes into 0x9b78A81836bda21CAaA368d935A09EFB1B86316c, has full minting power over $LEX. 

This snapshot vote serves to gauge sentiment among $LEX holders on minting an allocation for LexDAO Coop. purposes.
